    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "1 - [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "There appears to be no advantage to our continuing our",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "yearly review of captioned matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "In 1958 we adopted the practice of once a year reviewing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "complaints received concerning existence of flying saucers for the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "purpose of determining whether instructions in addition to those",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "already issued to the field were necessary. The last memorandum",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "dated 10/2/62 pointed out that our policy concerning unidentified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "flying objects was to conduct no investigation when received in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "the field but the field should submit the facts immediately to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the Air Force. Our SAC Letters dated in 1949 and in 1952 emphasized",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the afore-mentioned policy and it does not appear that at this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "time further instructions to the field are necessary.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "During the past 12 months we have received no complaints",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "regarding flying saucers and during the past 24 months only one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "complaint was received, the facts of which were immediately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "referred to the Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "ACTION:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Since it does not appear that continuation of our yearly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "review of the flying saucer situation is warranted, no further",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "analysis or review of matters coming within this field will be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "conducted in the future. Action with respect to any complaints",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "received, of course, will follow our policy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
